Entries.default: "You see that I am occupied, yes?"
"Splendid! I could not be better, aimico."
Entries.female: "Splendid! I could not be better, aimica."

Entries.default: "The Roparu, they are wanting for a taste of real culture. You know?"
He coughs, knuckles pressed to his lips.
"You were speaking to me, eh? Go on then."
With a sniff, she turns away.
She steeples her fingers over her chest and sighs.
"The scent is rank, no? You are smelling the filth of the classes."
His lips curl in clear distaste.
